headline: RBC Capital Lifts Gilead Sciences (GILD) PT to $95 On Insights From a 2022 Patient Survey
summary: Gilead Sciences Inc. (NASDAQ:GILD) is one of the 11 most profitable NASDAQ stocks to buy now. On June 11, RBC Capital increased its price target for Gilead Sciences to $95 from $92, while maintaining a Sector Perform rating.
